Subject: drm/i915/display: Move psr related module parameters under display
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 942d654171bdaf41bc5c298857c5a342031d8154
